<plot>On the day before Sonny is to propose to his seemingly perfect girlfriend Monica, his best friend Hotbox returns for one night having spent the last 3 months 'partying like the Diddy in Cuba.' Hotbox informs Sonny he wants him to accompany him on his Cuban adventure. Now, with the help of his lovable yet clueless father, Sonny has one night to decide whether to enter his 30's as a married man or one with an uncertain future.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?612073</url></doc>
